  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n      \t\t\t\t\t\u003cul\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli id=\"Entry1\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cspan\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003ca name=\"entry\" id=\"EntryAnchor\"\u003eanchor\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/90/90de372a7a04e091225d61b6ae5f60dc.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\" title=\"Image rendering courtesy Saudi Arabia Holding Co\" data-size=\"3000x1688\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cimg srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/90/90de372a7a04e091225d61b6ae5f60dc.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/90/90de372a7a04e091225d61b6ae5f60dc.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/90/90de372a7a04e091225d61b6ae5f60dc.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\" src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/90/90de372a7a04e091225d61b6ae5f60dc.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" title=\"Image rendering courtesy Saudi Arabia Holding Co\" alt=\"Image rendering courtesy Saudi Arabia Holding Co\" width=\"514\" height=\"\"/\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eImage rendering courtesy Saudi Arabia Holding Co\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eBidding has started for the important project management role for the \u0026#39;North Pole\u0026#39; central business district that will accompany \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/fosterandpartners\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eFoster + Partners\u003c/a\u003e’ design for a 2-kilometer (appx. 1.2-mile) megatall tower—the world’s tallest—in \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/news/tag/1113779/riyadh\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eRiyadh\u003c/a\u003e. According to \u003ca href=\"https://www.globalconstructionreview.com/bidding-opens-for-saudi-arabias-2km-tall-tower/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eGlobal Construction Review\u003c/a\u003e, likely bidders include heavyweights \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/firms/cover/106465/aecom\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eAecom\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/firms/cover/22215861/bechtel-inc\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eBechtel\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/jacobs\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eJacobs\u003c/a\u003e, Parsons, Mace, and \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/firms/cover/9126568/turner-construction-company\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eTurner Construction\u003c/a\u003e (the latter having just been announced for the same role in the shorter \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/news/tag/722553/jeddah-tower\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eJeddah Tower\u003c/a\u003e—to which it is considered a \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/news/article/150418872/foster-partners-reportedly-designing-world-s-tallest-building-a-1-2-mile-high-riyadh-skyscraper\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ecompetitor\u003c/a\u003e).\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe outlet also reported that the project is to be named \u0026#39;Rise Tower\u0026#39; and located near King Khalid International Airport, which was also master planned by Foster + Partners.\u003c/p\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cbr clear=\"all\"/\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\u003ch2\u003eSimilar articles on Archinect that may interest you...\u003c/h2\u003e\n\t\t\u